ConnectionType_QParam.description:
The technical protocol (e.g., hl7-fhir-rest).

**Example object before encoding** 
```json
"connectionType": {
  "coding": [
    {
      "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/endpoint-connection-type",
      "code": "hl7-fhir-rest",
      "display": "HL7 FHIR"
    }
  ]
}

PayloadType_QParam.description:
Filter by the message standard or payload type supported by the Endpoint. Matches against Endpoint.payloadType.coding.code.

**Example object before encoding** 
```json
"payloadType": [
  {
    "coding": [
      {
      "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/endpoint-payload-type-epc",
      "code": "bars",
      "display": "BaRS"
      }
    ]
  }
]
```
